	(369,3,'lore-realinstruments','Lore: Real Instruments','2009-03-09',1,'','','image','Based on a Twitter post I made that got favorited a lot. Audience participation!\r\n\r\nAlso: Dark \'N\' Stormy. Fill highball glass with ice. Add one shot dark rum, fill with ginger beer, garnish with lime slice.'),
