	(432,3,'lore-drivingschool','Lore: Driving School','2009-06-10',1,'','','image','Pi&ntilde;a colada: blend 1 shot white rum, 1 shot coconut cream, and 3 oz. pineapple juice with crushed ice. Serve in hurricane glass with pineapple slice and maraschino cherry.'),
	(433,1,'doubleact','The Comedy Double-Act Name Generator','2009-06-11',0,'','','html','I actually wrote the original script behind this for my own use, to pick a name for a pair of upcoming characters. Some folks on Twitter wanted to see it in action, and that led, circuitously but inevitably, here.'),
	(434,4,'mm-dryad','Dryad','2009-06-12',1,'','','image','It always seems that in RPGs, when a dryad needs help it\'s because there\'s some threat involving axes and fire and evil humanoids. You never see a dryad asking for help with gall wasps or root fungus.\r\n<p>\r\nAnyhow, the point I\'m trying to make here is that if I had a tree that was part of my actual body, I would have some very particular ideas about what squirrels would be allowed to do with it.\r\n<p>\r\nNow that I think of it, I feel the same way about my real body, but it rarely comes up.'),
	(435,3,'lore-iwill','Lore: I Will','2009-06-15',1,'','','image','I registered qqcats.com. Not sure what I\'m going to do with it.'),
	(436,3,'lore-latestsong','Lore: Latest Song','2009-06-16',1,'','','image','Cosmopolitan: 1 shot vodka, pony shot Cointreau, juice of one lime, 1 oz. cranberry juice. Shake with ice and strain into a cocktail glass.'),
	(437,1,'robotjoke','A Robot Joke','2009-06-17',1,'','','image','I guess this is kind of turning into Random Joke Week. Okay then!\r\n<p>\r\nAlso: I very recommend <a href="http://www.darcomic.org/">Dar</a>, a great funny autobio comic by Erika Moen. There\'s cartoon nudity and sex talk there, so keep that in mind if you\'re not in a position to view such things.'),
